targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  'Value' AS "Property", -- Becomes table headers
  -- metadata -> 'papermill' ->> 'input_path' AS "Notebook",
  SUBSTRING(
        input_path, 
        POSITION('/./' IN input_path) + 3 -- Start after the last '/' in '/./'
    ) AS "Notebook",
  metadata -> 'papermill' ->> 'parameters' AS "Parameters",
  metadata -> 'papermill' ->> 'default_parameters' AS "Default parameters",
  metadata -> 'papermill' ->> 'environment_variables' AS "environment variables",
  metadata -> 'papermill' ->> 'version' AS "Papermill version",
  -- metadata -> 'papermill' ->> 'start_time' AS "Start",
  TO_CHAR(
    TO_TIMESTAMP(
        (metadata -> 'papermill' ->> 'start_time'),
        'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS'
      ),
      'DD Month YYYY at HH24:MI:SS'
    ) AS "Start time",
  -- metadata -> 'papermill' ->> 'end_time' AS "End",
  TO_CHAR(
    TO_TIMESTAMP(
        (metadata -> 'papermill' ->> 'end_time'),
        'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS'
      ),
      'DD Month YYYY at HH24:MI:SS'
    ) AS "End time",
  metadata -> 'papermill' ->> 'duration' AS "Duration (s)",
  metadata -> 'kernelspec' ->> 'name' AS "Kernel name",
  metadata -> 'kernelspec' ->> 'display_name' AS "Kernel display name",
  metadata -> 'kernelspec' ->> 'language' AS "Kernel language",
  metadata -> 'language_info' ->> 'version' AS "Kernel language version",
  metadata -> 'papermill' ->> 'exception' AS "Exception"
FROM
  (
    SELECT
      (output :: jsonb -> 'metadata') AS metadata,
      (output :: jsonb -> 'metadata' -> 'papermill' ->> 'input_path') AS input_path
    FROM
      reports_admin
    WHERE
      id = ${report_id}
  ) AS sub;
